data.description: ***SHORT SALE*** Come enjoy this wonderful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath 2007 craftsman lodged along a cul-de-sac in the Clearwood Community.  This home brings you a new A/C, new deck, new carpet, new paint, butcher block counter-top, and plenty of parking.  Clearwood offers 3 fishing lakes, 5 beaches, a community center with an in-ground pool and jacuzzi, covered BBQ areas along the lake, several playgrounds, and walking trails all around.  Clearwood is within minutes of the great Deschutes Waterfall and is a very common commute to JBLM. Come and check it out!
